The source for this book is stored on GitHub at <span><a href="https://github.com/gvwilson/teachtogether.tech" class="uri">https://github.com/gvwilson/teachtogether.tech</a></span>. If you know how to use Git and GitHub and would like to change, fix, or add something, please submit a <a class="glossref" href="#g:pull-request"><strong>pull request</strong></a> that modifies the LaTeX source in the <code>tex</code> directory. If you would like to preview your changes, please read the instructions in the <code>BUILD.md</code> file in the root directory of the project.
</li>
