</p>
</dd>
<dt>
Moshe
</dt>
<dd>
<p>
will cover part of this book in a two-day weekend workshop and study the rest on his own.
</p>
</dd>
<dt>
Samira
</dt>
<dd>
<p>
will use this book in a one-semester undergraduate course with assignments, a project, and a final exam.
</p>
</dd>
<dt>
Gene
</dt>
<dd>
<p>
